OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780942271
OL,3,CLast day of 2026 Royal Cornwall Show
OL,4,Ccancelled
OL,6,FThe final day of this year's Royal
OL,7,FCornwall Show has been cancelled.
OL,9,FOrganisers say after a thorough
OL,10,Fassessment of weather conditions on
OL,11,Fthe morning of Saturday 6 June,
OL,12,Fthey've cancelled the last day of the
OL,13,F2026 event.
OL,15,FThey say they understand the news will
OL,16,Fbe "disappointing", but safety remains
OL,17,Ftheir "highest priority". The Met
OL,18,FOffice has issued a yellow weather
OL,19,Fwarning for wind across the south west
OL,20,Ffrom 9am until 7pm.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
