OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780942271
OL,3,CLast day of 2026 Royal Cornwall Show
OL,4,Ccancelled
OL,6,FThe forecaster says winds could reach
OL,7,F50mph and there's the potential for
OL,8,Fdamage to temporary structures.
OL,10,FIn a statement, organisers of the
OL,11,FRoyal Cornwall Show said: "It is with
OL,12,Fgreat regret that following a thorough
OL,13,Fassessment of forecast weather
OL,14,Fconditions and their impact on the
OL,15,Fshowground, the difficult decision has
OL,16,Fbeen taken to cancel the final day of
OL,17,Fthe Royal Cornwall Show on Saturday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780942271
OL,3,CLast day of 2026 Royal Cornwall Show
OL,4,Ccancelled
OL,6,F"The safety and wellbeing of our
OL,7,Fvisitors, exhibitors, competitors,
OL,8,Fmembers, staff, volunteers and
OL,9,Fcontractors has been central to this
OL,10,Fdecision and remains our highest
OL,11,Fpriority.
OL,13,F"We recognise how disappointing this
OL,14,Fnews will be for everyone involved,
OL,15,Fparticularly those who had planned to
OL,16,Fattend, exhibit or compete, and we
OL,17,Fwould like to thank all our
OL,18,Fstakeholders for their patience,
OL,19,Funderstanding and support.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
